{"tid":1810311,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[狙擊] 天地有正氣 古有通識黃者 今有黑警王狗射尿","createTime":"2020-01-03T18:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T16:00:29.000Z","uid":40856,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"205ef63e7d4c6fb480be5c3a85446862ecc429dc","tid":1810311,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:16:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>都係個句啦 一見星CHING 就知一定有梁蛇出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n七年前 我老死建勳黑客叫雞一事 <br />\n我可以一手將佢捧為補習界既傳奇 成為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">通色黃者</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n四個月前 物理治療師袁子威冷血言論 <br />\n成功幫佢一夜間多左<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">成萬個網民想同佢屌眼做愛</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就知我星CHING戰績彪炳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢期黑警咁撚紅 梗係要推返一兩件啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正所謂<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">那裡有星CHING 那裡就有正義</span></strong></span><br />\n事緣早兩日有巴打貼左出黎 有黑警休班期間突然膀胱爆炸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1808878/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1808878/page/1</a><br />\n解決之際都不忙叫朋友拍片 影低痾尿既英姿<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">完美演繹 王狗射尿（王俊浩）</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n片（好彩我back up 得快咋 差D冇得睇）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dcsEqcoNdjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdcsEqcoNdjs&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=a6966442\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dcsEqcoNdjs</a><br />\n<br />\n另外 條片得九秒其實唔係好過癮 所以我整左一連三條GIF 等大家欣賞<br />\n因為又細又黑 乜都睇唔到 所以係出得街架 連仔唔好BAM我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DL20RKR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDL20RKR.gif&h=6513b9b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HR3O0Db.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHR3O0Db.gif&h=781e2045&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35YZ7ic.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35YZ7ic.gif&h=eec5e618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家有冇發現 王犬小便時 係舉前足既</span></strong></span><br />\nFROM: 老豆搵仔 A700＋王蛇拍片朋友（大家快手BACK UP）"},{"pid":"341d7a1c3e80b136a4132cb2f7c42302d2085538","tid":1810311,"uid":40856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:16:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">天地有正氣 KEITH LEUNG愛叫雞</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cb89509096c9e44e89a47dc43f9bb2574c6e69bd","tid":1810311,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0816b8b5dc78c8afd730e9713ba8aec53916ebdb","tid":1810311,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacd9c7445a6c85d9d625e30e27a53e2ea3d979f","tid":1810311,"uid":71031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28c3e44ed8c1cf181233d14ce96a125b55f77d2","tid":1810311,"uid":189486,"like":0,